libhinawa (0.7.0-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * debian/control
    - set Architecture: linux-any for all package to avoid build with non-linux
      arch (Closes: #823011).
    - bump standars-version to 3.9.8.
    - add 'Uploaders' field.
  * debian/watch
    - support cryptographic signature verification.

